## Agent Endpoints

Once the function app is running, the following endpoints are available:

- Invoke agent: `POST http://localhost:7071/api/echo_agent/invoke`
- Stream agent: `POST http://localhost:7071/api/echo_agent/stream`
- Health check: `GET http://localhost:7071/api/echo_agent/health`
